Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.68,0:00:02.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.94,0:00:09.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好苦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.94,0:00:11.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你那是什麼表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.36,0:00:15.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那不是咖啡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.53,0:00:17.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,美奈不是喝不了咖啡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.70,0:00:19.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼要買那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.04,0:00:24.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也差不多要成為大人了 以為自己能喝就買了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:26.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.42,0:00:33.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你哪裡像大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.22,0:00:36.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就算是我也有很多地方有成長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.55,0:00:39.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那早苗就能喝了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.64,0:00:42.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我能喝啊 而且還是黑咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.19,0:00:48.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,黑咖啡…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.73,0:00:53.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個換給你喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.03,0:00:57.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是 我是大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.37,0:00:58.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.74,0:00:59.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.03,0:01:00.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.24,0:01:01.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,快換給我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.66,0:01:03.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.00,0:01:10.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.92,0:01:12.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.55,0:01:15.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嘛 也有喝不了咖啡的大人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:17.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不過你還是個小孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.34,0:01:19.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.73,0:01:31.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,大人可不會幹這種事
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,——op——
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:17.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天又被高木同學捉弄了一整天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:28.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不過 明天一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:29.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:33.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:35.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:37.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天一個人走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:38.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:40.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼 一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:41.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.12,0:03:45.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:47.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:50.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是高木同學不是騎車嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:51.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我推著就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.79,0:03:55.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,空罐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:03.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那罐果汁 是最近新推出的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:04.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:06.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:08.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這難道是什麼陷阱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:09.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,很好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:11.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你要不要嘗一口
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:12.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:13.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:17.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:21.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 雖然我不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:25.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣其實是間接接吻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:28.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哼哼哼 怎麼樣啊 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:31.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不好意思了吧 你就難為情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:34.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:37.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她一點也不難為情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.09,0:04:39.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個人究竟怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:42.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,給你 謝謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.26,0:04:43.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真好喝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:53.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:56.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喝啊 我完全不介意的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:05:00.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒什麼 這點小事不算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:06.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是間接接吻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:14.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:18.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我看看 垃圾桶在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:20.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.13,0:05:23.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哇哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:26.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片 你還真能投進去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:29.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一順手就投出去了 沒想到竟然能投中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:43.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我原來還有這種才能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:47.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好 我也來試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.67,0:06:01.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你往哪裡扔啊 根本搆不到嘛高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:04.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那你要和我比賽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:06.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,比賽？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:09.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,無所謂 反正我是不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.39,0:06:13.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼我們輪流投 先投進者為勝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:18.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,竟然發起沒有勝算的挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.23,0:06:21.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看來高木同學已經氣昏頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:24.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這感覺真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:28.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是高木同學贏了 你要我做什麼我都聽你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:30.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我可聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:32.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,待會兒不准反悔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:33.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.41,0:06:36.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不過我不會輸就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.41,0:06:39.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我要扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.71,0:06:42.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.05,0:06:52.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是你沒投中 就是我的勝利了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:58.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,又被她擺了一道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:03.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,站在剛才的位置上 用同樣的角度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:07.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:11.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我能行 我一定能投進去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.62,0:07:13.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:15.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是西片贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:18.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我就把我的初吻給你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.68,0:07:33.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:35.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:36.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:38.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你還問是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:39.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就在我投的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:41.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:43.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:46.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好的 要遵守約定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:48.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要讓你幹什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:58.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 她想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.83,0:07:59.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:03.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就算不讓你做什麼也沒什麼不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:04.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.05,0:08:09.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 高木同學 那不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:11.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你這樣做的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:13.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我感覺我一輩子都沒辦法贏過你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:14.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那就有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:16.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,反正你也贏不了我 這不挺好的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:20.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你這是什麼意思啊 我說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.77,0:08:22.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,碳酸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:28.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太辣舌頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:28.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}此處日語的「辛い」，專指食物對口腔舌頭的刺激、刺痛感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.69,0:08:30.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你那是什麼表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:31.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那不是碳酸汽水嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.24,0:08:34.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,美奈不是喝不了碳酸汽水嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.33,0:08:40.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,碳酸為什麼會這麼辣舌頭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.50,0:08:43.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼總買些自己喝不了的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:45.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,又在裝大人了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:48.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才不是呢 我喜歡這個味道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:08:53.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「嗡」地一下來勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:08:53.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}日語「ツンてきた」，意為某些味道對鼻腔的強烈刺激後的表情、反應
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:55.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我的舌頭 我的舌頭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:56.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你真吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.26,0:09:00.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,由加莉喝了碳酸汽水之後也會這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.39,0:09:01.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:03.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那你喝喝看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:04.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:09.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,腦子絕對會「嗡」的一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:11.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不會啦 不會啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:21.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,其實是來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.00,0:09:23.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:27.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「嗡」的一下究竟是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.38,0:09:29.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的會有那種反應嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:32.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不好 想打嗝了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.76,0:09:34.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有反應了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.09,0:09:39.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在這種時候打嗝肯定會被她們嘲笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:46.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是我快要忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:50.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,已經忍不住了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:56.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,又「嗡」地來勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:01.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,幹嘛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:03.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:07.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:13.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼 明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:20.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,給我走著瞧 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:23.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,加上回家路上被捉弄的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:26.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天被她捉弄了十五次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:30.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在比賽中出現失誤的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.77,0:10:34.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,作為給自己的懲罰 我會進行十倍的練習
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:38.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我相信這樣做能讓我在下一次奪取勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.41,0:10:40.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.74,0:10:44.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是被捉弄了十五次 乘上十倍就是一百五十次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:48.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,第一次做的話 沒什麼難度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:51.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,總之先做三倍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:58.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一 二 三 四…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:01.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,十八
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.51,0:11:04.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,十九
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.10,0:11:09.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,二十…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:12.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,比想像中難多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.02,0:11:14.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,稍微減少一點次數吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:15.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:20.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這是給平日被捉弄了太多次的自己的懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:28.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一邊體會痛苦 一邊提高警惕防止下次重蹈覆轍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:30.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,加油啊 我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.29,0:11:33.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,肌肉鍛鍊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:40.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你的手臂怎麼了 受傷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:44.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒什麼 只是普通的肌肉酸痛罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:46.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:51.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,別這樣 真的很疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:54.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,剛剛的要算一次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:57.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這時我應該對自己嚴格一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:11:59.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就記一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:07.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,被騙了吧 肌肉酸痛挺嚴重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:11.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這次是的的確確地被捉弄了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.37,0:12:15.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼突然肌肉酸痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:18.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那個 我從昨天開始鍛鍊肌肉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:21.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 要是不三天打魚兩天曬網就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:25.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哼 你就儘管說吧 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:33.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼 今天被高木同學捉弄的次數是二十三次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:36.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這不是比昨天還多了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:42.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一 二 三…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:45.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,話說回來 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:46.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你還在堅持鍛鍊肌肉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:48.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 姑且有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:51.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誒 你真的堅持下來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:54.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,託你的福
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:12:55.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不過你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:12:57.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:13:01.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,據說成長期時肌肉鍛鍊過度的話會長不高哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:05.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:08.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,話說回來 我也好像在哪裡聽說過…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.39,0:13:09.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:12.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是讓高木同學長得比我還高的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.18,0:13:14.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那她不就會更變本加厲地捉弄我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:16.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.98,0:13:20.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不過那好像只是謠言而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.82,0:13:21.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,原來是謠言嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.65,0:13:26.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不如說 適度的肌肉鍛鍊可以促進身高發育呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:31.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是這樣 所以你就安心繼續鍛鍊肌肉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.25,0:13:33.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我覺得這樣很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:36.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雖然只有一點點 但感覺你比以前變得結實了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.09,0:13:40.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:46.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 一言不發的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:50.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道說你害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:52.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,害 害羞什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:54.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你臉紅了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.64,0:13:58.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,果然 你害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:01.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是的 你幹嘛總是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.11,0:14:04.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,都說了 因為你的反應很有意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:08.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不過 你比以前結實了是實話哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.57,0:14:11.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,變得有點帥氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:15.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你的臉比剛才更紅了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.04,0:14:18.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是這樣的 是因為天氣太熱了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:20.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等等 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:21.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我說 等等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:23.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,到頭來 今天被她捉弄了五十四次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:26.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,算上剛剛那次就是五十五次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.59,0:14:30.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不過 我決定就算不被高木同學捉弄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:32.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,也要堅持鍛鍊肌肉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:35.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,配音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:40.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喬尼先生 今晚要不要來咱家吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:42.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哎呀 這要看工作忙不忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:45.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是很晚才能下班 我就和次郎吃了再回來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:50.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雖然和次郎打好關係也不錯 偶爾也來一下咱家嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:52.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,人家最近很寂寞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.87,0:14:55.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是我要工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:14:58.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,差不多該回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:01.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼 再玩一會兒也沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.46,0:15:04.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼要講關西腔啊 聽到就煩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:08.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太過分了 你一點也不在乎人家的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:11.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你這麼說也太小氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:13.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也是很拼命的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.93,0:15:16.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你哭什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.02,0:15:20.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為 喬尼先生和次郎都陷入工作無法自拔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.90,0:15:23.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,人家已經不能忍耐下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:25.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,突然變成修羅場了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.28,0:15:28.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 真是麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:31.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太過分了 太過分了喬尼先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:34.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是你是這種態度的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:36.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我就不管你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:38.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:43.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那兩隻貓 都是公的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:47.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那 應該叫喬尼前輩才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.92,0:15:50.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,呀 這不是次郎嗎 一起去吃飯如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:54.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,回家吧 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.51,0:15:57.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,傘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:09.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,竟然在放學時開始下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:12.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼 我可沒聽說今天會下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.53,0:16:14.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我沒帶雨衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.87,0:16:15.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,冒失鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:19.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早苗 你對美奈太嚴格啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.62,0:16:22.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我們搭巴士回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:24.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我沒帶錢搭巴士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:26.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,超級冒失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.34,0:16:27.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:29.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我借給你吧 巴士票而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:35.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡 今天也被捉弄得夠嗆的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:39.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不回家嗎 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:43.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那個 我忘帶傘和雨衣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:49.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你還真是冒失啊 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:51.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不知道今天會下雨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.95,0:16:53.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的太冒失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:16:59.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,竟然沒有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:03.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我記得西片的傘挺大的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.04,0:17:05.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.25,0:17:12.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這就是所謂的相合傘嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.67,0:17:14.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼會發生這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:17.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不好 感覺這樣好尷尬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:19.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:21.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,說些什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.27,0:17:25.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學 你的自行車怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:27.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我明天走路上學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:29.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.86,0:17:35.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感覺剛才的氣氛尷尬的要命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:38.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感覺要窒息了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:41.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不趕緊做些什麼緩和這種氣氛的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:49.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.09,0:17:50.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:53.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:55.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,被嚇到了吧 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:00.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:02.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:05.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡 不愧是高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:07.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這種程度的惡作劇…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.90,0:18:09.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼濕噠噠的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.78,0:18:15.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你太大驚小怪了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.95,0:18:25.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,話說回來 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:27.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你那邊的肩膀淋濕了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:29.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,只淋濕了一點兒 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:32.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不行 會感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:35.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,再湊近一點 好好地躲到傘下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:48.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,心臟跳動的聲音 好大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:51.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.36,0:18:56.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是被高木同學發現我很緊張 她一定會來捉弄我的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.61,0:18:59.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,總之 不說些什麼的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.37,0:19:01.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:02.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.12,0:19:07.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學竟然忘記帶傘 真是少見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.46,0:19:11.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道說 高木同學出人意料地是個冒失鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.59,0:19:15.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道我說得太過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.84,0:19:20.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.43,0:19:22.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我可能也有些健忘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:27.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學承認自己有些健忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:30.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這是什麼展開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:33.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感覺自己好像贏了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.94,0:19:36.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,剛才我也忘了一件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:38.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣嗎 忘了事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.95,0:19:40.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是什麼事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.07,0:19:45.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,像現在這樣 形容兩個人打著同一把傘走路的情形
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:47.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是叫什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.75,0:19:48.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.91,0:19:51.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我有點想不起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:54.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.84,0:19:56.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是叫什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:19:59.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,相合傘…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.47,0:20:01.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.18,0:20:03.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我聽不到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.97,0:20:09.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.35,0:20:11.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是相合傘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:14.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你肯定沒有忘記吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:15.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:17.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那個是叫什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.15,0:20:24.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,情侶之間為了表達愛意 用自己的嘴唇去接觸對方嘴唇那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.66,0:20:27.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡 答不上來就輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.66,0:20:30.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,親 親吻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.75,0:20:33.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼 雨聲太大 我聽不見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:36.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雨勢已經比剛才小了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.59,0:20:39.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不要裝作沒聽見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.13,0:20:41.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是親吻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.93,0:20:43.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 是的是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.93,0:20:48.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,還有 不是有情侶用來表達心情的詞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.27,0:20:50.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:53.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你看 就是那個比「喜歡」更進一步的詞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:54.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.98,0:20:57.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,開頭的第一個字是「a」的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.98,0:20:57.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}這裡高木想說的詞是日語的「我愛你」 即愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.61,0:20:59.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我不知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.24,0:21:02.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,下一個字是「i」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:04.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我猜不出來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:06.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼 換成英文的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.49,0:21:09.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是「I」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:11.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,接下來是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.12,0:21:18.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「I」「lo」的下一個字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:21.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你說說看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.38,0:21:22.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,已經夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:24.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,最後一個字是「you」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:26.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,都說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.35,0:21:30.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:40.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雨停了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.15,0:21:42.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.40,0:21:46.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太好了 我還以為要堅持到高木同學家門口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.49,0:21:47.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,害得我提心弔膽的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:50.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.04,0:21:52.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我走這邊回去 再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.79,0:21:58.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我忘記回家的路了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.63,0:22:03.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是的 饒了我吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPJP——
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.90,0:01:37.53,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}勘違いされちゃったっていいよ、君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:41.91,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて思ってたって言わないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.95,0:01:52.25,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}近づく空の香りを隣で感じていたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.71,0:02:01.10,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}校庭で君のことを一番に見つけて今日は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.14,0:02:09.35,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて話しかけようか？ ちょっと考えるの楽しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:12.32,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}風に揺らされるカーテン
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.11,0:02:17.70,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不意打ちに当たる日差し
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:21.62,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}眩しそうな顔を笑ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:25.50,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}照れて伏せちゃうのね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.41,0:02:33.59,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}憂鬱なテストも吹き飛ばせるような
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.75,0:02:41.89,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ねえ、二人で秘密の約束をしたいなって提案です
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.26,0:02:47.31,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}勘違いされちゃったっていいよ、君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:51.31,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて思ってたって言わないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.31,0:03:01.53,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}近づく空の香りを隣で感じていたいの
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPCH——
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.90,0:01:37.53,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}會錯意了也沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:41.91,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}和你一起就是幸福 這樣想著卻不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.95,0:01:52.25,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}瀰漫在周圍的那陣幽香 想在你的身邊靜靜感受
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.71,0:02:01.10,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}在校園的庭院 第一個發現你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.14,0:02:09.35,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}今天要和你說些什麼呢 即便是想著這些也是一種樂趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:12.32,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}窗簾隨風起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.11,0:02:17.70,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不經意地投入一束陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:21.62,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你那美麗的容顏笑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:25.50,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}羞得我抬不起頭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.41,0:02:33.59,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}風兒喧囂 似要吹散考試的憂鬱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.75,0:02:41.89,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}吶 我想要和你一起 立下兩人的秘密約定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.26,0:02:47.31,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}會錯意了也沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:51.31,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}和你一起就是幸福 這樣想著卻不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.31,0:03:01.53,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}瀰漫在周圍的那陣幽香 想在你的身邊靜靜感受
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——EDJP——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.06,0:22:28.87,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}「目を覚ましてよ」 君の声が僕を包み Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.91,0:22:37.25,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}窓を開けて　そよ風が君の髪をなびく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.58,0:22:41.67,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}部屋から出る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.67,0:22:48.34,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}僕の腕をつかみながら　君は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.43,0:22:57.44,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}「もう少しだけ」「もう少しだけ」と 僕に　君は呟く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.44,0:23:09.53,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}この世界が闇に染まる前に この思いを
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.57,0:23:17.29,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}だからお願い　僕の傍にいてくれないか
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.33,0:23:19.62,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}君が好きだから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.62,0:23:25.05,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}この思いが君に届くように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.05,0:23:30.51,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}願いが叶いますように
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——EDCH——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.06,0:22:28.87,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}「起床了哦」你的聲音環繞著我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.91,0:22:37.25,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}推開窗戶 你的秀髮隨微風飄揚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.58,0:22:41.67,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}走出房間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.67,0:22:48.34,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你挽著我的手臂 輕聲呢喃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.43,0:22:57.44,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}「再陪我一會兒 再陪我一會兒」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.44,0:23:09.53,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}我要把這思念傳達給你 在世界被染上黑暗之前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.57,0:23:17.29,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}所以拜託了 請留在我身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.33,0:23:19.62,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}因為我是如此地愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.62,0:23:25.05,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}願這思念能傳達到你的心裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.05,0:23:30.51,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}希望這一切都能化為現實
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——STAFF——
